      <title>Missing Semester Lecture1: Course Overview + The Shell</title>
      <link href="/2024/04/15/missing-semester-lecture1/"/>
      <url>/2024/04/15/missing-semester-lecture1/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="Lecture-1-Course-Overview-The-Shell"><a href="#Lecture-1-Course-Overview-The-Shell" class="headerlink" title="Lecture 1: Course Overview + The Shell"></a>Lecture 1: Course Overview + The Shell</h3><p><a href="https://missing.csail.mit.edu/2020/course-shell/">https://missing.csail.mit.edu/2020/course-shell/</a></p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">mv</span> a.md b.md</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><blockquote><p>rename the file</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">mv</span> a.md ../b.md</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><blockquote><p>move the file</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">rm</span> dir1</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><blockquote><p>delete all items recursive</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">rmdir</span> dir1</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><blockquote><p>delete dir only empty</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">ls</span> ..</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><blockquote><p>list all files of the father dir</p></blockquote><p>shortcut: <code>Control + L</code></p><blockquote><p>same as command clear</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cat</span> &lt; hello.txt &gt; hello2.txt</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><blockquote><p>replace hello2.txt with the content of hello.txt</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cat</span> &lt; hello.txt &gt;&gt; hello2.txt</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><blockquote><p>append the content of hello.txt to hello2.txt as an appendix</p></blockquote><ul><li><strong>Pipe</strong></li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">ls</span> - l | <span class="built_in">tail</span> -n1</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><blockquote><p>get last info of (ls -l)</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">curl --<span class="built_in">head</span> --silent google.com | grep -i content-length</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><blockquote><p>output is ‘Content-Length:219’</p></blockquote>]]></content>
      
      
